title: ExeScript v3.0.zip
description:
ExeScript.v3.0
 

ExeScript is a program that converts batch files 
(.bat), VBScript, JavaScript, WSF, WSH and HTA 
scripts to executable files (.exe) in less than 30 
seconds. It also protects contents of bat, .vbs, 
.js, .wsf, .wsh and .hta files from being changed 
by other users accidentally or intentionally. In 
addition, ExeScript hides contents of these files, 
so they cannot be viewed. This means that all 
actions are executed by batch, Visual Basic, 
JScript, WSF, WSH and HTA files will remain unknown 
and cannot be used to crack or reverse-engineer the


scan with keygen - http://www.virustotal.com/analisis/c384c5cf6a7bad3eb703d8ee82c63bc8
